                  <accMat>
                     <p>There are two AM-slips, (a) and (b), found in the manuscript informing about
                        possible scribes of the manuscript. Slip (a) reads: <q xml:lang="is"
                           >Bryniolfr Einarsson seger, ad þessa <lb/>
                           <hi rend="underline">Ragnars Saga</hi> se hverki skrifud <lb/> af <hi
                              rend="underline">Kolbeine Han<ex>n</ex>essyne nie</hi> Ple (α) <lb/>
                           Sveinssyne. Og verd eg þ ad <lb/> corrigera þad, sem eg (in registro
                           <lb/> qvodam) hefi skrifad um hnd<lb rend="hyphenated"/>ena ä <hi
                              rend="underline">Ragnars Sgu</hi> og <hi rend="underline">Expli<lb
                                 rend="hyphenated"/>catione Sigurdrïfumla</hi> i bők <lb/>
                              þe<ex>ss</ex>e er eg feck fra Þorlake <lb/> Þordarsyne; Item <hi
                              rend="underline">Sgubokinne</hi>
                           <lb/> sem stendr in Bibliotheca Re<lb rend="hyphenated"/>Seniana pag.
                           259. α] Sr. Gisle Alfsson helldr þő fyr<lb rend="hyphenated"/>er vïst ad
                           þetta sie hnd Pls <lb/> Sveinssonar. Seger og <add place="above"
                              >ad</add> hnd Pls <lb/> hafi umbreitst j þvi Ple hafi <pb/> daprast
                           siőn, og kunni þvi tvennar <lb/> hans hendur őlïkar ad vera.</q>
                     </p>
                     <p>AM-slip (b) reads: <q xml:lang="is">
                           <del rend="overstrike">Þetta</del>
                           <handShift/>
                           <add place="above">þesse Ragnars Saga</add>
                           <handShift/>er med hende Kol<lb/>beins Hanneßonar ij <lb/> Flöa.
                           <handShift/> þat <lb/> mun <lb/> ei svo <lb/> vera. <lb/> þetta <lb/> mun
                           vera hnd Päls <lb/> Sveinssonar. <lb/> Bryniolfur Einarsson seger <lb/>
                           Nei. þ<ex>ad</ex> er vist ad þ<ex>ess</ex>e <lb/> sama hnd hefur
                              skrif<lb rend="hyphenated"/>ad f<ex>yrer</ex> Sr. Þorstein
                           Bins<lb/>son. vide titul ä þan<ex>n</ex>
                           <lb/> fragmentis folio, er eg <lb/> feck af Isleife Einars<lb
                              rend="hyphenated"/>syne, og tt hafde Þora <lb/> ä Setberge. hvar ä
                              Sup<lb rend="hyphenated"/>postitia Skilldunga <lb/> Saga.</q>
                     </p>
